        "Description": "Hillary Maxwell is among the conspirators involved in the Epstein scandal. In exchange for her freedom Maxwell provided the defense department intel on foreign operatives living in the United States.\r\rThe intelligence turned out to be a wild goose chase. Mrs. Maxwell has fled the states, but one of our operatives in Morroco has tracked her down to Marrakesh. \r\rFind her and eliminate her. We need to send a message to the Epstein Collective: Neither income nor influence will protect them.",
